{"tid":822973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風啲廢老真係唔好出街","createTime":"2018-09-16T14:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T18:44:12.000Z","uid":142518,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8293efe3bb08eb3a3dff2604cd329789228b7735","tid":822973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"頭先落去買老麥<br />\n排隊條人龍已經長到乜咁<br />\n買完飛佢話要等一個鐘先有嘢食<br />\n老麥職員本身已經好忙<br />\n仲有個廢老喺度攪事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =m記職員   ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =廢老<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哥仔幫我查吓得未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望一望佢張飛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你張飛幾時買㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：半個鐘之前買嘅咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：未得啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指住顯示屏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：佢冇編號啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：等多陣先會有，宜家咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：有冇搞撚錯，你地而家冇顯示呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：.... ，214號、4212號<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你咩服務態度呀，宜家點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續好忙咁做嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續喺度嘈<br />\n<br />\n好心你啦，人地已經同你解釋咗要等幾耐<br />\n佢哋10號風球已經仲要返工<br />\n又要受你哋啲垃圾脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打風就留係屋企啦仲要出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係一陣又多咗件長者失蹤人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強烈要求打風啲廢老真係唔好出街"},{"pid":"2f4d8a8e111e86c0e4990393488d5ff4b9358960","tid":822973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"應該要立法禁止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3635ee5bbaab9c19704455b2f12edb1c0d06725","tid":822973,"uid":157501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"我本身想去買<br />\n但見你話好撚多人<br />\n我都怕我個區多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db71e273a4a596e269ce8a390d49c2c48f25805","tid":822973,"uid":142518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3635ee5bbaab9c19704455b2f12edb1c0d06725","tid":822973,"uid":157501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"我本身想去買<br />\n但見你話好撚多人<br />\n我都怕我個區多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"唔使諗一定好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ce1650931141e1833919ace3553eb84c123f9d","tid":822973,"uid":157501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5db71e273a4a596e269ce8a390d49c2c48f25805","tid":822973,"uid":142518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3635ee5bbaab9c19704455b2f12edb1c0d06725","tid":822973,"uid":157501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"我本身想去買<br />\n但見你話好撚多人<br />\n我都怕我個區多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/